text: Nipponaphera kastoroae is a species of sea snail, a marine gastropod mollusk in the family Cancellariidae, the nutmeg snails. ==References== == Further reading == * Bouchet P. & Petit R. E. (2008). "New species and new records of southwest Pacific Cancellariidae". The Nautilus 122(1): 1-18. Category:Cancellariidae Category:Gastropods described in 1997
title: Nipponaphera kastoroae
